"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"我希望有相当多的人可以继续认为比特币的结局是郁金香。投资品只有在最具有争议的时候才最具有投资价值，投资回报率才会越高。如果大家都认为是好的东西比如黄金，全部人都达成共识，那么他的潜在涨幅就会很小。如果一样投资品所有人都认为是垃圾，那么基本上他就是没有投资价值。往往争议比较大的，最具有投资性，潜在的风险不小但回报率巨大。\",\"timestamp\":1639710019,\"title\":\"比特币的结局是否会像郁金香一样?\"},\"digest\":\"jo1LK80YjWUHWGmRXdweVBvkWy7M2M_7Oc0CrgYp8_4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x20fd78931f71d8D6D4BbC0E9e2D02a69cbd5BBB9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"NbB4kYCpeShLqtPWhpLfifjukO5uopV8OCZH1StQeGc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"sChg-16vGTOaDAwMyo-M7bARJPUuc0f6qU1EhtTC3e8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"JzYJik77jU-0LOzhGQxShPLFW5NzmR6ZEAWtCqx45dVlkVLY1GiF_JGOjQo9tUfmLOJ2i7psbRclnniP2NpRSg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd599ad6742f232b6af7f4216f0d35d431cf0b6816bb44cea3c3f52fb5bfaef1f43ab5c4f056ef9530db11f668a18817d0ed72a7bea143a7c996186631cb981dc1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"NbB4kYCpeShLqtPWhpLfifjukO5uopV8OCZH1StQeGc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"sChg-16vGTOaDAwMyo-M7bARJPUuc0f6qU1EhtTC3e8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"jo1LK80YjWUHWGmRXdweVBvkWy7M2M_7Oc0CrgYp8_4\"}"